The evidence with the title 'Trump twists jobs numbers - factcheck.org ' says Mar 16, 2017  ... Trump boasted, “in the first two job reports since i took the oath of office, we've already added nearly half a million new jobs.” But only one of those  ... Since the election. As we have noted previously, the economy added more than 250,000 new jobs a month in 20 of the 96 months under president Obama. 
